sentence: Among the underlying components of the Russell 3000 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in LogMeIn Inc (Symbol: LOGM), where a total of 7,191 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 719,100 underlying shares.
That amounts to about 61.4% of LOGM's average daily trading volume over the past month of 1.2 million shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $75 strike put option expiring August 17, 2018 , with 6,788 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 678,800 underlying shares of LOGM.

Home Depot Inc (Symbol: HD) saw options trading volume of 19,609 contracts, representing approximately 2.0 million underlying shares or approximately 60.6% of HD's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 3.2 million shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $200 strike call option expiring August 17, 2018 , with 1,539 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 153,900 underlying shares of HD.

Particularly high volume was seen for the $16 strike put option expiring August 17, 2018 , with 3,069 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 306,900 underlying shares of GME.
